description:
Tober Brandt returns from a long hiatus to take on rookie Chad Brock. Chad's got the size advantage, but Tober's got the attitude to win. These guys hold nothing back as they fight for the win - ball grabbing, ass fingering and face sitting are all fair game.
SPECIAL MATCH:
The winner gets to chain up the loser and flog him mercilessly.
title: Tober's Back!
